REG:2017-04-12248
NAME:HUSSEIN HUSSEIN M
TITLE:JOB APPLICATION

Abstract
This software (KAZIRO) will be dealing with advertising job opportunities that are available in different organization both public and private sector.
This will give room applicants to apply for a job with respect to the opportunities that are available. It will be a web based application software.


Potential Users
I expect  potential users of my software to  be public and private sector like ministry,companies and others. But also the applicants for whom the system will require them to create account and provide information like their personal information,CVS's,experience and so on.

Aims and Goals
To create a very user friendly environment that will link companies and applicants in ensuring hiring process is easy such that all their hiring information are managed and centralized by this syetem.

